408    private function writeLegend(Chart $chart): void
409    {
410        // chart:legend
411        $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:legend');
412        switch ($chart->getLegend()->getPosition()) {
413            case Chart\Legend::POSITION_BOTTOM:
414                $position = 'bottom';
415                break;
416            case Chart\Legend::POSITION_LEFT:
417                $position = 'start';
418                break;
419            case Chart\Legend::POSITION_TOP:
420                $position = 'top';
421                break;
422            case Chart\Legend::POSITION_TOPRIGHT:
423                $position = 'top-end';
424                break;
425            case Chart\Legend::POSITION_RIGHT:
426            default:
427                $position = 'end';
428                break;
429        }
430        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:legend-position', $position);
431        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('svg:x', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($chart->getLegend()->getOffsetX()), 3) . 'cm');
432        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('svg:y', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($chart->getLegend()->getOffsetY()), 3) . 'cm');
433        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:legend-expansion', 'high');
434        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:style-name', 'styleLegend');
435        // > chart:legend
436        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
437    }

462    /**
463     * @throws \Exception
464     */
465    private function writePlotArea(Chart $chart): void
466    {
467        $chartType = $chart->getPlotArea()->getType();
468
469        // chart:plot-area
470        $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:plot-area');
471        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:style-name', 'stylePlotArea');
472        if ($chartType instanceof Bar3D || $chartType instanceof Pie3D) {
473            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('dr3d:ambient-color', '#cccccc');
474            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('dr3d:lighting-mode', 'true');
475        }
476        if ($chartType instanceof Bar3D || $chartType instanceof Pie3D) {
477            // dr3d:light
478            $arrayLight = [
479                ['#808080', '(0 0 1)', 'false', 'true'],
480                ['#666666', '(0.2 0.4 1)', 'true', 'false'],
481                ['#808080', '(0 0 1)', 'false', 'false'],
482                ['#808080', '(0 0 1)', 'false', 'false'],
483                ['#808080', '(0 0 1)', 'false', 'false'],
484                ['#808080', '(0 0 1)', 'false', 'false'],
485                ['#808080', '(0 0 1)', 'false', 'false'],
486            ];
487            foreach ($arrayLight as $light) {
488                $this->xmlContent->startElement('dr3d:light');
489                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('dr3d:diffuse-color', $light[0]);
490                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('dr3d:direction', $light[1]);
491                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('dr3d:enabled', $light[2]);
492                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('dr3d:specular', $light[3]);
493                $this->xmlContent->endElement();
494            }
495        }
496
497        //**** Axis ****
498        $this->writeAxis($chart);
499
500        //**** Series ****
501        $this->rangeCol = 'B';
502        $this->numSeries = 0;
503        foreach ($chartType->getSeries() as $series) {
504            $this->writeSeries($chart, $series);
505            ++$this->rangeCol;
506            ++$this->numSeries;
507        }
508
509        //**** Wall ****
510        $this->writeWall();
511        //**** Floor ****
512        $this->writeFloor();
513        // > chart:plot-area
514        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
515    }

517    /**
518     * @throws \Exception
519     *
520     * @see : http://books.evc-cit.info/odbook/ch08.html#chart-plot-area-section
521     */
522    private function writePlotAreaStyle(Chart $chart): void
523    {
524        $chartType = $chart->getPlotArea()->getType();
525
526        // style:style
527        $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:style');
528        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:name', 'stylePlotArea');
529        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:family', 'chart');
530        // style:text-properties
531        $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:chart-properties');
532        if ($chartType instanceof Bar3D) {
533            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:three-dimensional', 'true');
534            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:right-angled-axes', 'true');
535        } elseif ($chartType instanceof Pie3D) {
536            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:three-dimensional', 'true');
537            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:right-angled-axes', 'true');
538        }
539        if ($chartType instanceof AbstractTypeBar) {
540            $chartVertical = 'false';
541            if (AbstractTypeBar::DIRECTION_HORIZONTAL == $chartType->getBarDirection()) {
542                $chartVertical = 'true';
543            }
544            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:vertical', $chartVertical);
545            if (Bar::GROUPING_CLUSTERED == $chartType->getBarGrouping()) {
546                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:stacked', 'false');
547                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:overlap', '0');
548            } elseif (Bar::GROUPING_STACKED == $chartType->getBarGrouping()) {
549                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:stacked', 'true');
550                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:overlap', '100');
551            } elseif (Bar::GROUPING_PERCENTSTACKED == $chartType->getBarGrouping()) {
552                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:stacked', 'true');
553                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:overlap', '100');
554                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:percentage', 'true');
555            }
556        }
557        $labelFormat = 'value';
558        if ($chartType instanceof AbstractTypeBar) {
559            if (Bar::GROUPING_PERCENTSTACKED == $chartType->getBarGrouping()) {
560                $labelFormat = 'percentage';
561            }
562        }
563        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:data-label-number', $labelFormat);
564
565        // > style:text-properties
566        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
567        // > style:style
568        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
569    }

571    /**
572     * @throws \Exception
573     */
574    private function writeSeries(Chart $chart, Chart\Series $series): void
575    {
576        $chartType = $chart->getPlotArea()->getType();
577
578        $numRange = count($series->getValues());
579        // chart:series
580        $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:series');
581        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:values-cell-range-address', 'table-local.$' . $this->rangeCol . '$2:.$' . $this->rangeCol . '$' . ($numRange + 1));
582        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:label-cell-address', 'table-local.$' . $this->rangeCol . '$1');
583        // if ($chartType instanceof Area) {
584        //     $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:class', 'chart:area');
585        // } elseif ($chartType instanceof AbstractTypeBar) {
586        //     $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:class', 'chart:bar');
587        // } elseif ($chartType instanceof Line) {
588        //     $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:class', 'chart:line');
589        // } elseif ($chartType instanceof AbstractTypePie) {
590        //     $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:class', 'chart:circle');
591        // } elseif ($chartType instanceof Scatter) {
592        //     $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:class', 'chart:scatter');
593        // }
594        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:style-name', 'styleSeries' . $this->numSeries);
595        if ($chartType instanceof Area || $chartType instanceof AbstractTypeBar || $chartType instanceof Line || $chartType instanceof Scatter) {
596            $dataPointFills = $series->getDataPointFills();
597
598            $incRepeat = $numRange;
599            if (!empty($dataPointFills)) {
600                $inc = 0;
601                $incRepeat = 1;
602                $newFill = new Fill();
603                do {
604                    if ($series->getDataPointFill($inc)->getHashCode() !== $newFill->getHashCode()) {
605                        // chart:data-point
606                        $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:data-point');
607                        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:repeated', $incRepeat);
608                        // > chart:data-point
609                        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
610                        $incRepeat = 1;
611
612                        // chart:data-point
613                        $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:data-point');
614                        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:style-name', 'styleSeries' . $this->numSeries . '_' . $inc);
615                        // > chart:data-point
616                        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
617                    }
618                    ++$inc;
619                    ++$incRepeat;
620                } while ($inc < $numRange);
621                --$incRepeat;
622            }
623            // chart:data-point
624            $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:data-point');
625            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:repeated', $incRepeat);
626            // > chart:data-point
627            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
628        } elseif ($chartType instanceof AbstractTypePie) {
629            $count = count($series->getDataPointFills());
630            for ($inc = 0; $inc < $count; ++$inc) {
631                // chart:data-point
632                $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:data-point');
633                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:style-name', 'styleSeries' . $this->numSeries . '_' . $inc);
634                // > chart:data-point
635                $this->xmlContent->endElement();
636            }
637        }
638
639        // > chart:series
640        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
641    }
642
643    /**
644     * @throws \Exception
645     */
646    private function writeSeriesStyle(Chart $chart, Chart\Series $series): void
647    {
648        $chartType = $chart->getPlotArea()->getType();
649
650        // style:style
651        $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:style');
652        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:name', 'styleSeries' . $this->numSeries);
653        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:family', 'chart');
654        // style:chart-properties
655        $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:chart-properties');
656        if ($series->hasShowValue()) {
657            if ($series->hasShowPercentage()) {
658                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:data-label-number', 'value-and-percentage');
659            } else {
660                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:data-label-number', 'value');
661            }
662        } else {
663            if ($series->hasShowPercentage()) {
664                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:data-label-number', 'percentage');
665            }
666        }
667        if ($series->hasShowCategoryName()) {
668            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:data-label-text', 'true');
669        }
670        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:label-position', 'center');
671        if ($chartType instanceof AbstractTypePie) {
672            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:pie-offset', $chartType->getExplosion());
673        }
674        if ($chartType instanceof Line || $chartType instanceof Scatter) {
675            $oMarker = $series->getMarker();
676            /*
677             * @link : http://www.datypic.com/sc/odf/a-chart_symbol-type.html
678             */
679            $this->xmlContent->writeAttributeIf(Chart\Marker::SYMBOL_NONE == $oMarker->getSymbol(), 'chart:symbol-type', 'none');
680            /*
681             * @link : http://www.datypic.com/sc/odf/a-chart_symbol-name.html
682             */
683            $this->xmlContent->writeAttributeIf(Chart\Marker::SYMBOL_NONE != $oMarker->getSymbol(), 'chart:symbol-type', 'named-symbol');
684            if (Chart\Marker::SYMBOL_NONE != $oMarker->getSymbol()) {
685                switch ($oMarker->getSymbol()) {
686                    case Chart\Marker::SYMBOL_DASH:
687                        $symbolName = 'horizontal-bar';
688                        break;
689                    case Chart\Marker::SYMBOL_DOT:
690                        $symbolName = 'circle';
691                        break;
692                    case Chart\Marker::SYMBOL_TRIANGLE:
693                        $symbolName = 'arrow-up';
694                        break;
695                    default:
696                        $symbolName = $oMarker->getSymbol();
697                        break;
698                }
699                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:symbol-name', $symbolName);
700                $symbolSize = number_format(CommonDrawing::pointsToCentimeters($oMarker->getSize()), 2, '.', '');
701                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:symbol-width', $symbolSize . 'cm');
702                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:symbol-height', $symbolSize . 'cm');
703            }
704        }
705
706        $separator = $series->getSeparator();
707        if (!empty($separator)) {
708            // style:chart-properties/chart:label-separator
709            $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:label-separator');
710            if (PHP_EOL == $separator) {
711                $this->xmlContent->writeRaw('<text:p><text:line-break /></text:p>');
712            } else {
713                $this->xmlContent->writeElement('text:p', $separator);
714            }
715            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
716        }
717
718        // > style:chart-properties
719        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
720        // style:graphic-properties
721        $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:graphic-properties');
722        if ($chartType instanceof Line || $chartType instanceof Scatter) {
723            $outlineWidth = '';
724            $outlineColor = '';
725
726            $oOutline = $series->getOutline();
727            if ($oOutline instanceof Outline) {
728                $outlineWidth = $oOutline->getWidth();
729                if (!empty($outlineWidth)) {
730                    $outlineWidth = number_format(CommonDrawing::pointsToCentimeters($outlineWidth), 3, '.', '');
731                }
732                $outlineColor = $oOutline->getFill()->getStartColor()->getRGB();
733            }
734            if (empty($outlineWidth)) {
735                $outlineWidth = '0.079';
736            }
737            if (empty($outlineColor)) {
738                $outlineColor = '4a7ebb';
739            }
740            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('svg:stroke-width', $outlineWidth . 'cm');
741            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('svg:stroke-color', '#' . $outlineColor);
742        } else {
743            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'none');
744            if (!($chartType instanceof Area)) {
745                $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('draw:fill', $series->getFill()->getFillType());
746            }
747        }
748        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('draw:fill-color', '#' . $series->getFill()->getStartColor()->getRGB());
749        // > style:graphic-properties
750        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
751        // style:text-properties
752        $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:text-properties');
753        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('fo:color', '#' . $series->getFont()->getColor()->getRGB());
754        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('fo:font-family', $series->getFont()->getName());
755        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('fo:font-size', $series->getFont()->getSize() . 'pt');
756        // > style:text-properties
757        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
758
759        // > style:style
760        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
761
762        foreach ($series->getDataPointFills() as $idx => $oFill) {
763            // style:style
764            $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:style');
765            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:name', 'styleSeries' . $this->numSeries . '_' . $idx);
766            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('style:family', 'chart');
767            // style:graphic-properties
768            $this->xmlContent->startElement('style:graphic-properties');
769            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('draw:fill', $oFill->getFillType());
770            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('draw:fill-color', '#' . $oFill->getStartColor()->getRGB());
771            // > style:graphic-properties
772            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
773            // > style:style
774            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
775        }
776    }
777
778    private function writeTable(): void
779    {
780        // table:table
781        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table');
782        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('table:name', 'table-local');
783
784        // table:table-columns
785        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-columns');
786        // table:table-column
787        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-column');
788        if (!empty($this->arrayData)) {
789            $rowFirst = reset($this->arrayData);
790            $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('table:number-columns-repeated', count($rowFirst) - 1);
791        }
792        // > table:table-column
793        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
794        // > table:table-columns
795        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
796
797        // table:table-header-columns
798        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-header-columns');
799        // table:table-column
800        $this->xmlContent->writeElement('table:table-column');
801        // > table:table-header-columns
802        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
803
804        // table:table-rows
805        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-rows');
806        if (empty($this->arrayData)) {
807            $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-row');
808            $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-cell');
809            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
810            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
811        } else {
812            foreach ($this->arrayData as $row) {
813                // table:table-row
814                $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-row');
815                foreach ($row as $cell) {
816                    // table:table-cell
817                    $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-cell');
818
819                    $cellNumeric = is_numeric($cell);
820                    $this->xmlContent->writeAttributeIf(!$cellNumeric, 'office:value-type', 'string');
821                    $this->xmlContent->writeAttributeIf($cellNumeric, 'office:value-type', 'float');
822                    $this->xmlContent->writeAttributeIf($cellNumeric, 'office:value', $cell);
823                    // text:p
824                    $this->xmlContent->startElement('text:p');
825                    $this->xmlContent->text($cell);
826                    // > text:p
827                    $this->xmlContent->endElement();
828                    // > table:table-cell
829                    $this->xmlContent->endElement();
830                }
831                // > table:table-row
832                $this->xmlContent->endElement();
833            }
834        }
835        // > table:table-rows
836        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
837
838        // table:table-header-rows
839        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-header-rows');
840        // table:table-row
841        $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-row');
842        if (empty($this->arrayData)) {
843            $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-cell');
844            $this->xmlContent->endElement();
845        } else {
846            $rowFirst = reset($this->arrayData);
847            foreach ($rowFirst as $key => $cell) {
848                // table:table-cell
849                $this->xmlContent->startElement('table:table-cell');
850                if (isset($this->arrayTitle[$key - 1])) {
851                    $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('office:value-type', 'string');
852                }
853                // text:p
854                $this->xmlContent->startElement('text:p');
855                if (isset($this->arrayTitle[$key - 1])) {
856                    $this->xmlContent->text($this->arrayTitle[$key - 1]);
857                }
858                // > text:p
859                $this->xmlContent->endElement();
860                // > table:table-cell
861                $this->xmlContent->endElement();
862            }
863        }
864        // > table:table-row
865        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
866        // > table:table-header-rows
867        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
868
869        // > table:table
870        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
871    }

873    private function writeTitle(Title $oTitle): void
874    {
875        if (!$oTitle->isVisible()) {
876            return;
877        }
878        // chart:title
879        $this->xmlContent->startElement('chart:title');
880        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('svg:x', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($oTitle->getOffsetX()), 3) . 'cm');
881        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('svg:y', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters($oTitle->getOffsetY()), 3) . 'cm');
882        $this->xmlContent->writeAttribute('chart:style-name', 'styleTitle');
883        // > text:p
884        $this->xmlContent->startElement('text:p');
885        $this->xmlContent->text($oTitle->getText());
886        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
887        // > chart:title
888        $this->xmlContent->endElement();
889    }
